# Records docs/demo.gif from the scripted replay in docs/demo_replay.py.
# Regenerate with: vhs docs/demo.tape (requires vhs: brew install vhs)

Output docs/demo.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1000
Set Height 650
Set Padding 16
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type "python3 docs/demo_replay.py"
Enter
Show

Sleep 33s
